<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr">
<div class="govspeak">
<p>This information outlines the statutory guidance and policies for independent schools to help you meet your legal responsibilities and obligations.</p>

<h2 id="independent-schools">
<span class="number">1. </span>Independent schools</h2>

<h3 id="managing-staff">
<span class="number">1.1 </span>Managing staff</h3>

<ul>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/staffing-and-employment-advice-for-schools">Staffing and employment advice for schools</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/disqualification-under-the-childcare-act-2006">Childcare Disqualification</a></p>
</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="running-a-school">
<span class="number">1.2 </span>Running a school</h3>

<ul>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-complaints-procedures">Complaints procedure statement</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/data-protection-and-privacy-privacy-notices">Data protection and privacy notices</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/data-protection-toolkit-for-schools">Data protection toolkit for schools</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/health-and-safety-advice-for-schools">Health and safety</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/standards-for-school-premises">Premises management documents</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/good-estate-management-for-schools/the-fundamentals-of-good-estate-management">Guidance on good estate management</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-attendance">Register of pupils’ admission to school and attendance</a></p>
</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="pupil-welfare">
<span class="number">1.3 </span>Pupil welfare</h3>

<ul>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/keeping-children-safe-in-education--2">Child protection – safeguarding</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/behaviour-and-discipline-in-schools-guidance-for-governing-bodies">School behaviour and discipline</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-exclusion">School Exclusion</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/send-code-of-practice-0-to-25">Special educational needs and accessibility plan</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/supporting-pupils-at-school-with-medical-conditions--3">Supporting pupils with medical conditions</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

